== Potential Causes ==
* Interrupted updates;
* [[Malware_and_Firmware_Trojans|malware]] ([[Malware_and_Firmware_Trojans#Valid_Compromise_Indicators_versus_Invalid_Compromise_Indicators|less likely]]); 
* [[Troubleshooting#Hardware_Issues|hardware issues]];
* bugs (either in {{project_name_long}} or any components it is based on);
* user misconfiguration;
* third-party software introduced issued.

== Potential Problem Solutions ==
Options:

* '''A)''' Become knowledge about the Linux boot process and debugging;
* '''B)''' Hire a sysadmin to fix this;
* '''C)''' [[Factory Reset]].

The knowledge on how to fix Linux boot issues is a general Linux sysadmin skill and [[unspecific|unspecific to {{project_name_short}}]].

Some pointers can be found on the [[Recovery]] wiki page.

